examples.en: The prince was transformed into an ugly animal.
They have transformed their home into a showplace.
Increased population has transformed the landscape.
She transformed the clay into a beautiful sculpture.
The world is being transformed by information technology.
A lanky kid transformed almost overnight into a handsome young man.
The inner layers of alburnum are gradually transformed into duramen.
He may be a working class boy at heart, but his lifestyle has been transformed.
The movie is a fantasy about a mousy housewife who is transformed into a glamorous star.
For the sake of their image, the band members transformed themselves from clean-cut lads to slovenly rockers.
